// Simple WarpScript example
// This example just returns a random value for testing purposes

// Token placeholder (will be replaced)
'${WARP_TOKEN}' 'token' STORE

// Generate a random value between 0 and 100
// In a real scenario, you would fetch actual metrics from Warp 10

RAND 100 *

// The value on top of the stack is what will be returned
// and compared against level thresholds
